Here, I’ve tested the relationship between length and boldness using a generalized linear model. With a p-value = 0.36, there is no evidence for relationship between length and boldness for this species. 

personality <- read.csv("personalitydata_generated.csv")
p1 <- glm(Boldness ~ Length, 
          data = personality,
          family = gaussian(link = "identity"))
summary(p1)
